<article>
  <header>
    <h2>About</h2>
  </header>
        
  <div class="two-col" id="right">
    <h3 class="sub-section-title">Finish Weekend MVPs</h3>
    <p>Finished! Check out the projects below that have been launched during @finishweekend.</p>
    <div id="slider">
      <a href="#" id="prev">slider-prev</a>
      <a href="#" id="next">slider-next</a>
      <a href="http://loseitorloseit.com"><%= image_tag "loseitorloseit.png" %></a>
    </div>
  </div>
        
  <div class="two-col" id="left">
    <h3 class="sub-section-title">Suggested Projects</h3>
    <p>Something that can be released in a weekend. Not a final version, but something to get it in front of people. Maybe you've been coding up a killer app, but need help building a website to announce it. Maybe you have a nasty bug you need help with. Maybe you need some copy written. Maybe you just need a few hours of encouragement. We'll get your project polished up and ready to go.<br>Bring a project, and get ready to ship it!</p>
  </div>
        
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</article><!-- #article -->

<article>
  <header>
    <h2>Sponsors</h2>
  </header>
        
  <p class="section-description">Supporting Finish Weekend</p>
  <%= render 'events/sponsors' %>
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</article><!-- #article -->
    
<article>
  <header>
    <h2>People</h2>
  </header>
        
  <p class="section-description">Your best buds will be there.</p>
        
  <div class="one-col">
    <ul id="people-list">
      <% @current_event.registrations.each do |person| %>
        <li><%= image_tag person.gravatar_url(:secure => true, :size => 25, :rating => "PG", :default => "https://www.finishweekend.com/missing.jpg"), :title => person.name %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </div>
        
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</article><!-- #article -->
    
<article>
  <header>
    <h2>Schedule</h2>
  </header>
        
  <p class="section-description">Productivity needs a plan.</p>
        
  <div class="three-col" id="right">
    <h3 class="sub-section-title">Important Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Sleeping/Lodging</strong>More information will be coming on other lodging...</p>
    <p>We'll provide ample amounts of food, drink, and caffeine. There are also lots of restaurants within walking distance.</p>
  </div>
        
  <div class="three-col" id="center">
    <h3 class="sub-section-title">2nd Day</h3>
    <p><strong>8:00</strong>Breakfast and refocus</p>
    <p><strong>3:00</strong>Show and tell about what we finished</p>
  </div>
        
  <div class="three-col" id="left">
    <h3 class="sub-section-title">1st Day</h3>
    <p><strong>8:00 – 8:45</strong>Coffee and donuts and getting setup</p>
    <p><strong>8:45 – 9:00</strong>Official kickoff and announcements of what we intend to finish over the weekend</p>
    <p><strong>12:00</strong>Food! Feed the brain</p>
    <p><strong>6:00</strong>More food</p>
  </div>
        
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</article><!-- #article -->

<article>
  <header>
    <h2>Coming to:</h2>
  </header>
        
  <p class="section-description">Heads up. Future @finishweekend events:</p>
       
       
  <% @upcoming.each do |event| %>      
    <div class="three-col" id="left">
      <h3 class="sub-section-title"><%= link_to event.name, new_event_registration_path(event) %></h3>
      <p><%= event.starts_at.strftime "%B" %></p>
    </div>
  <% end %>
                
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</article><!-- #article -->

